OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FThe economy is officially in
OL,6,Frecession, ITV News Business and
OL,7,FEconomics Editor Joel Hills explains
OL,8,Fwhat this means
OL,10,FThe UK economy has been in by a series
OL,11,Fof economic shocks in recent years,
OL,12,Fnone of which Rishi Sunak had any
OL,13,Fcontrol over.
OL,15,FHe couldn't have prevented COVID from
OL,16,Freaching British shores and he can't
OL,17,Fbe held accountable for Russia's
OL,18,Fdecision to invade Ukraine.
