OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FBut, last January, Rishi Sunak decided
OL,6,Fto stake his reputation on a pledge to
OL,7,Fgrow the economy. And at the end of
OL,8,Flast year, the economy found a reverse
OL,9,Fgear.
OL,11,FLabour is calling it "Rishi's
OL,12,Frecession." It's opportunistic, it's
OL,13,Fnot entirely fair but the prime
OL,14,Fminister did invite us to judge him on
OL,15,Fwhat happens to economic growth.
OL,17,FA general election is months away. is
OL,18,Fa campaign gift for the Tories' rivals.
