OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FNor has the fact that the UK workforce
OL,6,Fis smaller than it was before COVID,
OL,7,Fin part because there has been a sharp
OL,8,Frise in the number of people who
OL,9,Fcannot work because they are long-term
OL,10,Fsick.
OL,12,FBut here's the thing: when it comes to
OL,13,Fliving standards (which is what we
OL,14,Fshould care about most), it's not the
OL,15,Fsize of the economy that matters, it's
OL,16,Fthe amount of growth per person.
