OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FEarlier, I asked the chancellor why we
OL,6,Fare doing so badly.
OL,8,F"UK slips into recession" is a
OL,9,Fpotentially calamitous headline for
OL,10,Fthe government.
OL,12,FThe prime minister has made a
OL,13,Fpolitical pledge and, thus far, he has
OL,14,Ffailed to deliver.
OL,16,FEconomically, whether the UK economy
OL,17,Fcontracted or indeed grew slightly at
OL,18,Fthe end of 2023 is almost irrelevant.
