OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FThe facts that matter are the UK
OL,6,Feconomy has flat-lined for the last
OL,7,Ftwo years
OL,9,FAnd, if you look back, living
OL,10,Fstandards have barely improved for the
OL,11,Flast 15 years.
OL,13,FThese are the real predicament we need
OL,14,Four politicians to fix.
OL,16,FAnd if you speak to economists, many
OL,17,Fwill tell you that they are not sure
OL,18,Fthat Labour has the answers.
